annotationA: GH23527p; Protein binding; RNA 7-methylguanosine cap binding; eukaryotic initiation factor 4G binding; RNA cap binding; translation initiation factor activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: translational initiation
annotationB: Probable nucleoporin Nup54; Probable component of the nuclear pore complex, a complex required for the trafficking across the nuclear membrane (By similarity). May have a role in the organization of the inner nuclear membrane proteins at the nuclear envelope together with Nup154; Belongs to the NUP54 family
